# Course Page Creation
- Course catalog page of LMS application should be based on REACT
- Course catalog page should be responsive
- Use bootstrap cards and grid layouts to display available courses
- Dynamic course data must look for and consume a central 'course API' resource
- Always render a prominent "Popular Courses" container tracking options C1, C2, and C3
- Enforce debouncing logic on dynamic text search fields to throttle live backend API requests